__ Cantrip: Preserve _________________________ Cost: 5 _______________________

Use:  cantrip preserve                         Material Component: corpse
Use:  C preserve

The cantrip preserve is a minor magic of the sphere of alternation/necromancy.
When cast upon a corpse, the cantrip will prevent the corpse from rotting.
Useful for preserving the corpses of companions until they get a life.
